a:2:{s:7:"content";s:1010:"<p>Tom Lehrer, in the introduction to one of his songs, possibly <em>National Brotherhood Week</em>, complains that the only thing worse than people who say they can't communicate is that they won't shut up about it. The other side of that coin is that people who claim to be ace communicators make themselves hostages to fortune.</p>
